#: src/06_development_environment/01_project_configuration/06_synth.md:3
msgid ""
"`[synth]` section specifies the configuration for the `veryl synth` command, "
"which performs lightweight logic synthesis to estimate area, timing and "
"power."
msgstr ""
"`[synth]` セクションは、簡易的な論理合成を行って面積・タイミング・電力を見積"
"もる `veryl synth` コマンドの設定を指定します。"

#: src/06_development_environment/01_project_configuration/06_synth.md:6
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[synth]\n"
"top          = \"TopModule\"\n"
"library      = \"sky130\"\n"
"clock_freq   = 100.0\n"
"activity     = 0.1\n"
"timing_paths = 1\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```toml\n"
"[synth]\n"
"top          = \"TopModule\"\n"
"library      = \"sky130\"\n"
"clock_freq   = 100.0\n"
"activity     = 0.1\n"
"timing_paths = 1\n"
"```"

